04:17.745 --> 04:22.436
Department of Agriculture, and this station you're listening to, that make these get-togethers possible.

04:23.078 --> 04:28.330
This is Smokey and his pals, the Sons of the Pioneers, asking you to always remember...

04:28.310 --> 04:31.213
